{"tid":1075573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"柯 震 東 Ig 抒 情：「不會再愛了。」兼 且 鬧 爆 網 友","createTime":"2019-03-24T08:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T14:16:10.000Z","uid":215823,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd39108980e745aff429cdc4281bd124b6df97c","tid":1075573,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"柯震東連續於IG張貼4張相片，更寫上「Goodbye」引發Fans憂慮，之後他彷彿自問自答的對話：「人會變嗎？！這個世界給你的答案是&hellip;不會。那還要堅持嗎&hellip;我回答世界&hellip;我很痛苦。很痛苦？！&hellip;世界回答你&hellip;對不起&hellip;我很殘酷。」<br />\n<br />\n有網民於柯震東IG上挑釁留言問道：「毒戒了嗎？」柯震東反擊道：「早戒了！你個智障。」之後亦有人留言指他一切都是「咎由自取。」而柯震東則反譏對方：「成語好好。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBDaYYF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBDaYYF.png&h=9ab470d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNrWUw1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNrWUw1.png&h=33629c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28Z9u5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28Z9u5n.png&h=0b2dbca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b8a0c4c4c166ade11b9a0486374fdba825eb298","tid":1075573,"uid":174432,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"早戒了，你個智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbaacd4595c362596ee5596cfe55703f198f3e3","tid":1075573,"uid":208726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"878683de76fa97f4ba59993a4a1b68441283ef74","tid":1075573,"uid":220431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b8a0c4c4c166ade11b9a0486374fdba825eb298","tid":1075573,"uid":174432,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"早戒了，你個智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"